00:21:42.093 --> 00:21:45.138 position:50% align:center
Mariana, you were ecstatic, huh?

00:21:46.765 --> 00:21:47.682 position:50% align:center
[MARIANA]
Miss Mira.

00:21:47.766 --> 00:21:49.392 position:50% align:center
[MIRA]
Uh, yes?

